Mean BOLD time series were extracted for each participant and each atlas region. To obtain a time-resolved connectivity matrix between all pairs of brain regions, the phase of the BOLD time series of each region was estimated using the Hilbert transform. The phase coherence between regions n and p at time t was then assessed using the following formula\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
